If you are a fan of Milkyway actioners, stay away from this. Bad Blood is an utterly witless attempt to cash in on the Milkyway look and feel. Instead of buying this dreck, get yourself a copy of PTU, The Misson, Exiled, or Breaking News.
Another Great action flick from china - some amazing fight scenes . A must have for your eastern action collection .
